@baseUrl = http://127.0.0.1:8000
@contentType = application/json

### Intent routing: create event (requires Google credentials)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/llm/ask
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "question": "Schedule meeting tomorrow at 3pm for 30 minutes",
  "k": 5
}

### Intent routing: missing time + duration clarification
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/llm/ask
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "question": "Schedule planning session tomorrow",
  "k": 5
}

### Intent routing: provide time + duration for previous request
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/llm/ask
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "question": "At 4pm for 30 minutes",
  "k": 5
}

### Intent routing: query calendar (requires Google credentials)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/llm/ask
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "question": "What do I have this week?",
  "k": 5
}

### Intent routing: update event (requires Google credentials)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/llm/ask
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "question": "Move my meeting to Monday at 9am",
  "k": 5
}

### Intent routing: create delete target (requires Google credentials)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/llm/ask
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "question": "Schedule lunch with Sam tomorrow at noon for 60 minutes",
  "k": 5
}

### Intent routing: delete event (requires Google credentials)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/llm/ask
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "question": "Cancel lunch with Sam tomorrow at noon",
  "k": 5
}

### Intent routing: delete event confirmation (send after confirmation prompt)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/llm/ask
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "question": "yes",
  "k": 5
}

### Intent routing: create conflict target (requires Google credentials)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/llm/ask
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "question": "Schedule focus block tomorrow at 5pm for 30 minutes",
  "k": 5
}

### Intent routing: conflict scenario (requires an existing event at the same time)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/llm/ask
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "question": "Schedule demo call tomorrow at 5pm for 30 minutes",
  "k": 5
}

### Intent routing: resolve conflict (reply after conflict prompt)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/llm/ask
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "question": "At 6pm",
  "k": 5
}

